SilphCo_10F_Text_FloorSign::
    .string "SILPH CO.\n"
    .string "RESEARCH TERMINAL\p"
    .string "FILE: SOUL CONDENSATION\n"
    .string "STATUS: PROTOTYPE\p"
    .string "Field reports confirm\n"
    .string "trainers collect energy\n"
    .string "after POKéMON battles.\p"
    .string "Trainers call this\n"
    .string "energy \"Souls.\"\p"
    .string "Normally this energy\n"
    .string "disperses quickly.\p"
    .string "However…\n"
    .string "our instruments\n"
    .string "can detect it.\p"
    .string "With the correct\n"
    .string "focusing field…\p"
    .string "Souls can be\n"
    .string "stabilized.\p"
    .string "Once stabilized,\n"
    .string "they can be stored\n"
    .string "temporarily.\p"
    .string "Stored Souls can then\n"
    .string "be transferred back\n"
    .string "into POKéMON.\p"
    .string "This process appears\n"
    .string "to accelerate\n"
    .string "POKéMON growth.\p"
    .string "POKéMON CENTERS may\n"
    .string "already be performing\n"
    .string "a safe version\n"
    .string "of this process.\p"
    .string "WARNING:\p"
    .string "Forced extraction\n"
    .string "produces unstable\n"
    .string "Soul signatures.\p"
    .string "Excess extraction\n"
    .string "may cause permanent\n"
    .string "damage to POKéMON.\p"
    .string "Access to this research\n"
    .string "has been restricted.\p"
    .string "Unauthorized use\n"
    .string "is strictly prohibited.\p"
    .string "— SILPH RESEARCH DIVISION\p"
    .string "Someone has accessed\n"
    .string "this file recently…$"
